Package pt.ptcris

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ORCIDClient
    Interface that encapsulates the communication with the ORCID client for a specified user profile.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ORCIDClientImpl
    An implementation of the ORCID client interface built over the Degois client.
    PTCRISGrouper
    A generic activity grouper for the PTCRIS framework.
    PTCRISync
    An implementation of the PTCRISync synchronization service based on the version 0.4.3 of the specification, enhanced with minimal quality thresholds.
    PTCRISyncResult
    A class that encapsulates the result of the synchronization procedures for a particular work.
